keyValuePair.Value: Close, but no cigar, eh? What are your thoughts?

A real disappointment for everyone connected with %1s. Your boys did so well to reach the %3s Final but, on the day, %2s were a little too good for you. What happens now? Where does this team go from here?
It was close and I'm proud of the boys.

Getting to the Final was an achievement in itself. It was a narrow defeat and that's hard to take. No wonder some of the boys were in tears after the game. I'll pick them up and we'll go again. This is all part of the journey.
